ActAeronautics Act
SubjectInterim Order No. 3 Respecting Flight Deck Occupants
PrecisOrder approving INTERIM ORDER NO. 3 RESPECTING FLIGHT DECK OCCUPANTS, made by the Minister of Transport on April 22, 2015, in order to ensure that there is always a second person on the flight deck during the absence of a flight crew member.
